column1: This is the real world... Right?
Yep, looks like we're back all right.

You have successfully returned from the Jail.
Welcome back.
I don't think I'm seeing her...
Hey, Shorty! Get your ass over here!
Don't yell that in public, idiot!
I'm in front of you, inside Joker's phone.
Oh, did you change your outfits?

I'm still Mona. I just look like a cat in
this world.
So, you really weren't a raccoon.
Wait, why're you on his phone now?
Why am I... Because I'm an AI.
A, uhhh... That's that smart thing, right?

Futaba told us all about it. She's an
"artificial intelligence."
Why are you in my phone?
Because it was the closest one to me.
I have your phone to thank for that.

I was thrown into endless light. When I tracked
down Joker's scent, I ended up here.

So, since she's an AI, she turned into data
when she came to this world.
Zat mean you're livin' in his phone?

It is somewhat small, but it's cozy and has
everything I need. Care to join me?

Haha... I don't even have the energy for
a comeback right now.

Anyway, it's a big relief knowing you made it
out of there safely.

Hey, but what about those other people
we saw in there? Are they still... you know?

But I seriously doubt normal folks would be
able to fight against that.

Me too, but... If we charge in without a plan,
we're just going to wind up captured too.

I get what you're saying, but if we charge in
without a plan, we're just going to wind up
captured too.

A new part of the Metaverse has its own version
of a Palace that we access through EMMA...
It even has a ruler Shadow...

Odds are that something horrible is
happening right now.

You're right. Talking about this here is
no good.

Let's get to Leblanc. We'll hammer out our
course of action with everyone there.
It appears I cannot exit this phone.

When I came to this world, I connected to
the internet and learned a great many things...

But my memory is still erased. I also found
no means of data recovery.

Furthermore, I am stuck here. What should
I do next?

Also, introducing Sophia to everyone else'll
probably make the explanation easier.

Wonder how THAT'S gonna go over... Especially
when they hear all the Palace-type shit.

Yeah, we got ourselves a whole gang. One of
'em'll probably flip her wig over you, too.
